{"tid":632663,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"瑪莎拉蒂越線撞豐田三傷","createTime":"2018-04-17T15:09:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T00:57:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8e6d8433beeef9d437224c4404b0ed8d50f3ca80","tid":632663,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T15:09:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180417/20363750?_ga=2.11243444.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180417%2F20363750%3F_ga%3D2.11243444.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=kJKF5bKJ3bb1eMIg7r1iLxOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=be4b78d0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180417%2F20363750%3F_ga%3D2.11243444.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=0c70d725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180417/20363750?_ga=2.11243444.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n瑪莎拉蒂越線撞豐田三傷<br />\n<br />\n9.9K<br />\n港聞<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】曾發生多宗奪命車禍的大埔公路沙田嶺段，昨日再有意外。一輛巿值約140萬元的瑪莎拉蒂跑車沿大埔公路出九龍，其後突然失控越線與一輛豐田P牌車迎頭相撞，兩車司機及一名男童乘客僅輕傷，警方正調查意外起因。<br />\n<br />\n昨晨8時許，涉事39歲姓鄧男子駕駛紅色瑪莎拉蒂跑車，載同5歲男童沿大埔公路出九龍，途至近六合村對開突然失控，先越過對面線與一輛由49歲姓潘女子駕駛的P牌豐田房車迎頭對撞，兩車撞至打白鴿轉，掃毀路邊一排欄柱後始告停定，兩車車頭嚴重損毀，零件散落一地，幸車頭堅硬，撞擊力未傷及兩車司機及乘客，3人分別報稱胸口及頸部痛楚，由救護車一併送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180417/large/17la7p61.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180417%2Flarge%2F17la7p61.jpg&h=702bee47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n瑪莎拉蒂跑車（左）昨與豐田房車相撞，車頭嚴重損毀。周鴻熙攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大埔公路屢生意外<br />\n<br />\n意外發生後，由於有車輛撞爆水箱及漏出偈油，消防一度到場戒備，警方亦要封鎖肇事路段調查，現場來回線交通一度擠塞，至9時許路面清理完畢才恢復正常。<br />\n<br />\n大埔公路沙田嶺段經常生嚴重車禍，最近一宗為今年4月初，一名休班警駕駛私家車往沙田，至上址越線與電單車相撞，鐵騎士送院不治，司機涉危駕導致他人死亡被捕。<br />\n<br />\n■記者周鴻熙<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180417/large/17la7p62.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180417%2Flarge%2F17la7p62.jpg&h=fea4e9a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n與涉事跑車同款的瑪莎拉蒂Gran Turismo。互聯網"},{"pid":"961894ff9a47aee6d24caabf12a48fc6f5e149de","tid":632663,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T15:17:52.000Z","msg":"硬膠泛民打手LIKLN<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191003_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=3124d977&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F191008_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=ff15f2d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/10/201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F10%2F201929_ea3dc39ca0b2f6b5f17abddec1f0e9a4.png&h=27225035&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81be054add884a2dda30cb69d4cd1ec86be9b8b4","tid":632663,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T15:32:41.000Z","msg":"呢架maserati成日炒"},{"pid":"43a707e293a24ec49fb0dc9472df2ce95b09aab9","tid":632663,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T00:34:35.000Z","msg":"p牌女司機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6bfee3e1f834970b5ac5a71222995b4232469c9","tid":632663,"uid":38516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81be054add884a2dda30cb69d4cd1ec8